|--------|-------------|------------|-------------|
| **Revenue Generated** | $3.2M | {{revenue_generated}} | +172% |
| **Marketing Qualified Leads** | 18,450 | {{lead_count}} | +159% |
| **Sales Pipeline Value** | $12.5M | $28.4M | +127% |
| **Average Deal Size** | $18,500 | $24,200 | +31% |
| **Sales Cycle Length** | 87 days | 72 days | -17% |

