# Content Performance and Engagement

**Data-driven content strategy delivers results**

| Content Type | Pieces Created | Avg. Engagement | Lead Generation | Cost Per Lead |
|--------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------|---------------|
| **Whitepapers** | 8 | 847 downloads | 12,450 leads | $32.50 |
| **Webinars** | 12 | 285 attendees | 8,920 leads | $41.25 |
| **Case Studies** | 15 | 1,240 views | 6,780 leads | $67.80 |
| **Video Content** | 24 | 3,450 views | 11,200 leads | $28.90 |
| **Blog Posts** | 36 | 2,100 views | 8,482 leads | $45.70 |

**Video content achieved lowest cost per lead at $28.90**

@notes:
- Content variety engages different preferences
- Video content most cost-effective
- Whitepapers strong for lead generation
- Webinars provide high-value engagement
- Case studies build credibility

